<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY: IN DEFENSE OF COUNCIL HOPEFUL BARBARA YAROSLAVSKY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 As a person who has worked with Barbara Yaroslavsky on many different projects 
over the years, I can tell you firsthand of her inexhaustible energy when it 
comes to giving to the community. In no way is she anyone's puppet ("Police 
Union Pledges Support for D'Agostino in Council Race," Oct. 9).Her willingness 
to help or give time is her gift to you, no matter how big or small the 
request. In a city where people are preoccupied with their own needs and gains, 
you find in Barbara a person who genuinely and honestly cares. Her knowledge of 
current and pertinent issues that affect this community are a major priority 
with her. After all, that is really the most important issue, to care and work 
hard for the community we all share. 
</P>
<P>
 FRANCES TERRELL LIPPMAN 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles  
</P>
</TEXT>
