Town Square Shopping Center on Bristol Street between Sunflower Avenue and 
MacArthur Boulevard, in Laguna Niguel at Plaza de La Paz center on La Paz Road 
and in Mission Viejo at Portola Plaza on Los Aliso Boulevard and Santa 
Margarita Parkway.) 
