<P>
 Starting today, the northbound lane of California 23 in Fillmore will be 
closed from River Street to California 126 until Nov. 13. 
</P>
<P>
 The monthlong closure is needed during construction of the new $6-million 
Bardsdale Bridge over the Santa Clara River, Caltrans officials said. Bridge 
construction is expected to be completed by mid-December. 
</P>
