 La Verne's football team is ranked 25th in NCAA Division III heading into 
Saturday's Southern California Intercollegiate Athletic Conference game at 
Whittier. La Verne is 4-0. 
</P>
<P>
 Darren MacLellan gained 206 yards in La Verne's 23-6 victory over Cal Lutheran 
last weekend. MacLellan is the SCIAC's leading rusher with 649 yards in four 
games. 
