 Claremont-Mudd (1-3) plays host to Menlo in a nonconference game after last 
week's 49-28 SCIAC victory over Whittier. 
</P>
<P>
 John Shipp passed for 249 yards and three touchdowns and rushed for 115 yards 
and two scores. Shipp is averaging 291 yards a game in total offense, which 
ranks second in Division III. 
