<HEADLINE>
<P>
DIGEST: HART GETS ADDITIONAL TICKETS FOR CANYON GAME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 With tickets for Friday's football game between Hart and Canyon highs already 
sold out at Hart, Canyon officials Wednesday gave an additional 200 tickets to 
Hart.  
</P>
<P>
 A total of 4,000 tickets will be sold on an advance-only basis for the 
expected standing-room-only sellout at Canyon's stadium between the Foothill 
League rivals. 
</P>
<P>
 The 1,500 tickets allotted to visiting Hart were sold by Tuesday.  
</P>
<P>
 Canyon still had 600 of its 2,500 on Wednesday, when Bob Messina, Canyon 
associated student body director, gave up one-third of them. 
</P>
<P>
 Valley College (5-0) is ranked fifth in the state junior college football poll 
with Moorpark (3-1) 13th and Ventura (3-1) 16th. 
</P>
<P>
 Moorpark secured a berth among the top 20 with a 23-20 upset of Bakersfield on 
Saturday. 
</P>
