 MEXICAN STOCKS 
</P>
<P>
 * Mexican stocks posted their biggest one-day gain Wednesday since mid-July 
amid expectations of healthy third-quarter earnings. The Bolsa index soared 
2.82% to close at 2,740.82 points. 
</P>
